msgstr "Nebel|Schleier"

#: ../src/iop/hazeremoval.c:138
msgid "remove fog and atmospheric hazing from pictures"
msgstr "Entfernt Nebel und Dunstschleier"

#: ../src/iop/hazeremoval.c:255
